NG0504:795: srog chags lus dang mun par 'khyams //
NG0504:796: zas ni rigs pa yid dge sems /
NG0504:797: kha zas sna tshogs 'tsho bar byed //
NG0504:798: tshe ni nges med skad cig nas //
NG0504:799: bskal pa'i bar du thub pa yod /
NG0504:800: kha 'thor byol song rigs bzhi rgyu //
NG0504:801: gti mug btang snyoms mi dge dang *//
NG0504:802: dge ba spyad pa'i mthu stobs las //
NG0504:803: mi shes mun pa'i bsam gtan gyis //
NG0504:804: bya dang glang po sa srungs sogs //
NG0504:805: lha yi rigs kyi dud 'gror skyes //
NG0504:806: dge ba phra mo dngos logs pas //
NG0504:808: gti mug gsod gcod rdzun tshig gis //
NG0504:809: dmyal bar gnas pa'i dud 'gro ste //
NG0504:810: de rnams sems med sprul pa dang *//
NG0504:811: sems can blun rmongs gnyis yin no //
NG0504:812: phal cher gling bar mun pa dang *//
NG0504:813: sa 'og chu dang rgya mtsho gnas //
NG0504:814: rkang mang rkang med rkang gnyis dang *//
NG0504:815: rkang gcig rkang bzhi gzugs med yod //
NG0504:816: sdug bsngal mgon med dgra mang zhing *//
NG0504:819: ma bu nying sha rang sha za //
NG0504:820: gcig gis gcig 'joms za ba dang *//
NG0504:821: bkol spyod gsod rdung byed pa rnams //
NG0504:822: dngos su mthong yang mi go bas //
NG0504:823: glen zhing gti mug mun pas bsgribs //
NG0504:824: bya gcan ri dwags glang chen sogs //
NG0504:825: sha rus pags pa spu yi phyir //
NG0504:826: tshor ba'i sdug bsngal bsam mi khyab //
NG0504:827: nya thal chu srin sbrul gdug rnams //
NG0504:828: rang gis gzhan za gzhan gyis rang *//
NG0504:829: mang du 'dus pas gcig la za //
NG0504:830: gcig gis mang po'i gshed du byed //
NG0504:831: bya rog 'ug pa byi la khyi //
NG0504:832: zhe sdang las skyes sha za'i tshogs //
NG0504:833: wa dang spre'u bya byi srin //
NG0504:834: 'dod chags brnab sems sred pas sdug / nya dang phye leb bung ba bya //
NG0504:835: 'dod yon sdug bsngal grogs su mthong *//
NG0504:836: rta glang phag pa lug gi rigs //
NG0504:837: srin bu mngal gnas gti mug can //
NG0504:838: ri dwags sa bdag dngang skrag brgyal //
NG0504:839: rang snang dgrar langs srog 'chad yod //
NG0504:840: lus nad yid la zug rngu ni //
NG0504:843: lha mi las byol ngan song rtags //
NG0504:844: lus kyi phra rags rdul phran tsam //
NG0504:845: ri rab tsam gyi khyad par gyis //
NG0504:846: gzugs dang kha dog stobs khyad che //
NG0504:847: 'dod log zhe sdang gdug rtsub dang *//
NG0504:848: sbyin sogs phyin ci log song bas //
NG0504:849: dud 'gro'i rigs kyi gtso bo ni //
NG0504:850: klu bdag ba glang gdong pa can //
NG0504:851: mgo mjug sbrul la khog pa mi //
NG0504:853: rkyen sdug sbal sbrul 'jigs pas bskor //
NG0504:854: rgya mtsho chu mig ne'u gsing gnas //
NG0504:855: dkar phyogs dge ba bskyed pa rnams //
NG0504:856: bdud rtsi'i zas za longs spyod ldan //
NG0504:857: rdzu 'phrul stobs dang nus pa che //
NG0504:858: gnag phyogs gdug pa'i dug rlabs 'phro //
NG0504:859: gang dang lhan cig khros nas gnod //
NG0504:860: rang nad mdze sogs gzhan la dgod //
NG0504:861: na rag sdug bsngal cha re yod //
NG0504:862: zas su mi gtsang dri nga za //
NG0504:863: mkha' lding bye tshan char bab dang *//
NG0504:864: lha min khros pa'i chad pa yis //
NG0504:865: dmyal ba lta bu'i sdug bsngal yod //
NG0504:866: snga dro rdzu 'phrul sems gsal ldan //
NG0504:867: lha mi'i snang ba skabs su 'char //
NG0504:868: phyi dro gti mug dud 'gro yis //
NG0504:869: mun nag dug chu khol mar 'tshod //
NG0504:871: phrag dog mi dge'i rnam sems kyis //
NG0504:872: sha za khrag 'thung gzhan yul bcom //
NG0504:873: gnod sems dge dang 'dres par byed //
NG0504:874: gti mug smon pa phyin ci log / rgyamatsho'i nang song ri rab kyis //
NG0504:875: khong seng mun pas 'thibs pa ru //
NG0504:876: lha min dbang po sgra gcan 'dzin //
NG0504:877: bu dang chung mar bcas pa dang *//
NG0504:878: rin chen gzhal yas longs spyod dang *//
NG0504:879: tshal dang me tog 'bab chu'i steng *//
NG0504:880: bya dang bung ba'i tshogs kyis gang *//
NG0504:881: de ru skyes pa'i lha min rnams //
NG0504:882: shas cher dud 'gro'i bsam pa la //
NG0504:883: gzugs kyang dud 'gro'i mgo bo can //
NG0504:886: ri rab g.yo nus 'thab rtsod dga' //
NG0504:887: sdang sems skyes dus dmyal ba dngos //
NG0504:888: mi yi lo la zhag byas pa'i //
NG0504:889: bsgrangs pa'i rang lo lnga stong thub //
NG0504:891: 'phos tshe dmyal bar ltung ba mang *//
NG0504:892: de la sogs pa dud 'gro'i rigs //
NG0504:893: duhkha bshad pa brjod mi lang *//
NG0504:894: sbyin sogs dge las spyad byas kyang *//
NG0504:895: bsam pa ma rungs smon pas te //
NG0504:896: mi dge ba la bstod byas rgyus //
NG0504:897: lha min rigs ni rnam gnyis te //
NG0504:898: bdud rigs yi dwags rdzu 'phrul can //
NG0504:899: dud 'gro rigs su gtogs pa yin //
NG0504:901: rgya mtsho mtshams kyi ri rab logs la ni //
NG0504:902: rin chen gzhal yas dga' ba'i tshal dang bcas //
NG0504:903: ljon shing rdzing bu longs spyod sna tshogs ldan //
NG0504:904: lha min rgyal po dbang ston chung 'khor tshogs //
NG0504:905: sna tshogs sde rigs khri phrag bcu gnyis ni //
NG0504:906: gzugs ni sna tshogs bde sdug 'dres par spyod //
NG0504:907: dregs pa'i nga rgyal lha la rtsod 'dod cing *//
NG0504:908: rdzu 'phrul lus kyis nyi zla'i 'od kyang sgrib //
NG0504:909: ri bo g.yo dang gnam grum sgra skad sgrogs //
NG0504:910: rang lo drug stong dbang sgyur ba yin //
NG0504:911: sdig bcas mchod sbyin tshul chos rgyu yis skyed //
NG0504:912: grong khyer btses ldan ri rab log / grong khyer gnyis rtses brgya stong na //
NG0504:913: sngon bas lhag pa'i khang bzangs dang *//
NG0504:914: gser dang g.yer kha mi 'phreng tshal //
NG0504:915: 'dres pa'i tshal bzhi'i skyed tshal dang *//
NG0504:917: lha min bu mo rnams kyis mchod //
NG0504:918: stobs dang longs spyod dga' bar byed //
NG0504:919: lha min rang lo bdun stong thub //
NG0504:920: 'jig rten dge ba'i longs spyod kyis //
NG0504:921: gsum pa gser gyi sa gzhi'i steng *//
NG0504:922: grong khyer sum brtsegs can zhes pa //
NG0504:923: gser 'od ldan pa'i rin chen gyi //
NG0504:924: dpag tshad brgyad stong khang bzangs la //
NG0504:925: bkra shis rang mdzes chu rgyun dang *//
NG0504:926: shing ljon skyed tshal du ma la //
NG0504:927: bya dang bung ba'i tshogs kyis gang *//
NG0504:928: bdag nyid chen po thag bzangs rigs //
NG0504:929: lha min bu mo rab mdzes rnams //
NG0504:930: rin chen rgyan sras rtse dga' byed //
NG0504:932: stobs chen rab dgod nga rgyal rlom //
NG0504:933: lha min thams cad stags skyed cing *//
NG0504:934: longs spyod rtse rgod bag med spyod //
NG0504:935: tshe 'di rang lo stong phrag brgyad //
NG0504:936: de ltar lha min rigs rnams ni //
NG0504:937: dud 'gro rigs man ngan song gnas //
NG0504:938: 'phos te lha dang mir skyes kyang *//
NG0504:940: phral du dmyal bar ltung bar byed //
NG0504:941: chags sdang gnyis kyi sred pa yis //
NG0504:942: lha dang lha min 'thab rtsod rgyu //
NG0504:943: rkyen ni lha min bu mo yis //
NG0504:944: lha yi gnas su ltas pa las //
NG0504:945: lha yi bu rnams 'dod pa g.yos //
NG0504:946: lha yi bdud rtsi'i char phab pas //
NG0504:947: lha min rnams ni 'dod pa skyes //
NG0504:948: zas la chags shing mo la sred //
NG0504:949: mig ser phrag dog nga rgyal
NG0504:952: lha min sgra gcan dbang ldan khros //
NG0504:954: mi rnams dge spyod 'thab rtsod ni //
NG0504:955: dkar po'i klu rnams dga' ba yis //
NG0504:956: mi yul bkra shis bde legs 'byung *//
NG0504:957: 'dres spyod lha min nag tshogs tsam //
NG0504:959: mi rnams mi dge log spyad na //
NG0504:960: lha mi dpung skyed zhe khros nas //
NG0504:961: nag po'i klu dang ma mo yis //
NG0504:962: lo nyes nad yams 'khrug pa dang *//
NG0504:963: gangs chad chu rdol glog gi sgras //
NG0504:964: gling bzhi'i mi la 'tshe bar byed //
NG0504:965: dang po lha min rnams tshogs nas //
NG0504:966: nag po klu yi phyogs byas te //
NG0504:968: de rnams rgyal chen rigs bzhis 'joms //
NG0504:969: pham pas grong khyer gnyis pa yi //
NG0504:971: 'khor rnams sbran te go bgos nas //
NG0504:972: mi bzad g.yul 'gyed drag po la //
NG0504:973: rgyal chen bzhi yis pham par byas //
NG0504:974: de tshe grong khyer gsum pa yi //
NG0504:975: rab dgod thag bzangs dbang po khros //
NG0504:977: lha min rnams la stobs med cing *//
NG0504:978: lha min bu mo g.yo sgyu can //
NG0504:979: lha yi yid ni mi sdud dam //
NG0504:980: nor rgyas klu sogs nag po'i tshogs //
NG0504:981: tshar gcad bya phyir chas so zhes //
NG0504:982: lha min dbang pos kun la bsgos //
NG0504:983: lha min grong khyer sum brtsegs kyis //
NG0504:984: shing rta mtshon cha go bgos nas //
NG0504:985: bu mos lha bu mgo skor zhing *//
NG0504:986: rnga sgra lha min cha sgra yis //
NG0504:987: ri dang nags tshal mtsho rnams g.yos //
NG0504:988: de tshe lha rnams dga' ba'i tshal //
NG0504:989: lha dbang chos bzangs mdun sa nas //
NG0504:990: kun la bka' bsgos shing rta'i tshal //
NG0504:991: go cha 'dod phyir rgyug par byed //
NG0504:993: glang po chen po sa srungs bu //
NG0504:994: lus chen dpag tshad stong yod pa'i //
NG0504:995: mgo'i stong de stong ri rab stong *//
NG0504:996: de stengs lha yi dmag tshogs 'bum //
NG0504:997: bu mo mdzes mas rtse dga' byed //
NG0504:998: lha yi bu rnams rin chen brgyan //
NG0504:999: shing rta zhon nas mtshon cha thogs //
NG0504:1000: bar snang thams cad gang ba yis //
NG0504:1001: sgra chen sgrog cing dong bar byed //
NG0504:1002: de tshe stobs ldan nag po ma gtogs pa //
NG0504:1003: lha min thams cad spu zing byed //
NG0504:1004: lha min rnga sgras rgya mtsho 'gul //
NG0504:1005: klu rnams rgyugs pas sa gzhi g.yos //
NG0504:1006: gnod sbyin khros pas skar mda' ltung *//
NG0504:1007: 'jig rten skyong pas gling bzhi nyul //
NG0504:1008: dang po klu rnams dug char 'phen //
NG0504:1010: de tshe lha min dga' ba'i sgra //
NG0504:1011: ha ha 'byin cing rgyug par byed //
NG0504:1012: de la kun tu rgyu ba'i lha //
NG0504:1014: de la lha min ri bo 'phen //
NG0504:1015: thams cad mtshon cha'i char 'bebs byed //
NG0504:1016: de tshe lha rnams mtshon cha'i char //
NG0504:1017: phab pas ri ldeg rgya mtsho 'khrug / sgra ni
NG0504:1018: gnam sa grum mnyam grag / mtshon cha rdo rje
NG0504:1019: ser ltar bab // glog 'phreng bskal pa'i me 'od 'phro //
NG0504:1022: snying 'gas dran med phyogs bcur rgyug / de tshe rab dgod thag bzangs khros //
NG0504:1023: lha yi dbang po'i thog tu mchongs //
NG0504:1025: de la glang po sa srungs bus //
NG0504:1026: sna yi dbugs kyis 'gyel du bcug / rdo rje rmig pas phye mar brlags //
NG0504:1027: lha dbang sprul pas nam mkha' khengs //
NG0504:1028: gnam lcags char phab lha min bros //
NG0504:1029: sngon gyi bsad bcad rnam smin gyis //
NG0504:1030: la la smas shing la la shi //
NG0504:1031: lha min bu mo mya ngan byed //
NG0504:1032: smas shing mi dang mtshungs pa yin //
NG0504:1033: phrag dog gdug pa'i las 'bras kyis //
NG0504:1034: dngos po gang mthong go dang mtshon //
NG0504:1035: lus kyi las su gsod dang rtsod //
NG0504:1036: ngag tu rgyob dang sod sgra sgrogs //
NG0504:1037: yid la rtag tu dgra dang 'khrug / shi ba'i ro ni rgya mtshor skyur //
NG0504:1039: mgo dang sked pa ma chad na //
NG0504:1040: lus la mtshon bsnun rma yis ni //
NG0504:1042: rtag tu las kyi sdug bsngal spyod //
NG0504:1043: lha rnams srog gcod spangs pa yis //
NG0504:1045: lha rnams dga' ba'i tshal du bzlog / sdang sems med pas dga' bde spyod //
NG0504:1046: lha min rang yul 'thab rtsod byed //
NG0504:1047: ngan song sdug bsngal bsam mi khyab //
NG0504:1048: ma rig 'khrul kyang sbyin pa dang *//
NG0504:1049: tshul khrims dge bas las grub phyir //
NG0504:1050: gling bzhi dang ni gling phran gnas //
NG0504:1051: sgra mi snyan na dge ba'i mthus //
NG0504:1052: gzugs bzang khru ni sum cu gnyis //
NG0504:1053: rdzus skyes tshe lo stong thub cing *//
NG0504:1054: longs spyod 'dod lha bzhin du yod //
NG0504:1055: lus 'phags khru brgyad skyem byed legs //
NG0504:1056: drod skyes nyis brgya lnga bcu thub //
NG0504:1057: ba glang spyod pa khru bcu drug / sgong skyes lnga brgya longs spyod che //
NG0504:1058: 'dzam bu gling na khru bzhi pa //
NG0504:1059: mngal skyes lus kyi rig rtsal che //
NG0504:1060: tshe la nges med dpag med nas //
NG0504:1061: bar du brgyad khri tha ma bcu //
NG0504:1062: de las thung ba ma yi mngal //
NG0504:1063: gling bzhi tsam nas mngal skyes mang *//
NG0504:1064: dbyibs dang kha dog sa gzhi 'dra //
NG0504:1065: thun mong mi rtag skye shing can //
NG0504:1066: bsod nams las grub 'dzam bu sras //
NG0504:1067: las kyis sa par bshad pa 'di //
NG0504:1068: bskal ba dang nas tha ma'i bar //
NG0504:1069: dus kyi bzang ngan rim pa ru //
NG0504:1070: bde sdug gnyis la rim par spyod //
NG0504:1071: tshe lo dpag med brgyad khri'i dus //
NG0504:1072: mi yi gzugs gzung chags sdang chung *//
NG0504:1073: sgra mi snyan bzhin longs spyod che //
NG0504:1074: sa zhag ma rmos sa lu ljang *//
NG0504:1075: rtsol ba med pa'i longs spyod yod //
NG0504:1076: sde rigs khyim thab med par bde //
NG0504:1077: bar du las kyi chags sred kyis //
NG0504:1078: gsog 'jog btsal bas longs spyod nyams //
NG0504:1079: byang chub sems ldan kun don gyis //
NG0504:1080: rgyal po byung nas sde rigs dgos //
NG0504:1081: 'dod nyung btsun pas bram zer grags //
NG0504:1082: mkhas pa rje'u rigs phal pa dmangs //
NG0504:1083: ngan spyod snol bar grags pa bzhi //
NG0504:1084: las kyi rtsol bas longs spyod ldan //
NG0504:1087: bsod nams las la spyod pas bde //
NG0504:1088: de nas chags sdang dge sdig dran //
NG0504:1089: zug rngu las dbang cher song nas //
NG0504:1090: brgyad khri bcu par thub pa yi //
NG0504:1091: mu ge nad mtshon me chu rlung *//
NG0504:1092: lo zla zhag bdun go rims 'ong *//
NG0504:1093: dge bas dus kyi bskal pa bzang *//
NG0504:1094: bsod nams las byung gser zangs dngul //
NG0504:1095: lcags las grub pa'i 'khor lo yis //
NG0504:1096: sgyur rgyal mi yi dbang phyug po //
NG0504:1097: 'khor lo nor bu bud med de //
NG0504:1098: blon po dmag dpon glang chen bdun //
NG0504:1099: nye ba ral gri pags chen dang *//
NG0504:1100: tshal dang gos snam mal cha bdun //
NG0504:1101: longs spyod kun la dbang byed cing *//
NG0504:1102: sprul sku'i bstan pa rin chen sgron //
NG0504:1103: dge slong rnams ni 'byung ba'i phyir //
NG0504:1104: nyams pa med pa'i tshul khrims ldan //
NG0504:1105: de nas las dbang mi dge mthus //
NG0504:1106: tshe dang longs spyod stobs rnams bri //
NG0504:1107: gdul dka' 'dul ba'i dus la bab //
NG0504:1108: rgyal po sde dpon so sor 'byed //
NG0504:1109: bston pa'i chos la sde rigs gyes //
NG0504:1110: theg pa sna tshogs grub mtha' gcod //
NG0504:1111: spang blang bde sdug sna tshogs 'byung *//
NG0504:1112: gnyen po mi thub ngan dbang 'chor //
NG0504:1113: mi dge bcu sogs ngan spyod dus //
NG0504:1114: lnga bcu'i tshe la rtags tsam 'dzin //
NG0504:1115: bzhi bcu'i dus na bstan pa nub //
NG0504:1116: bde skyid zad pas ngan 'gror mtshungs //
NG0504:1117: de rnams dge sdig rnam smin gyis //
NG0504:1118: dbang gi 'bras bu thun mong dang *//
NG0504:1119: thun mong ma yin gang byas myong *//
NG0504:1120: sna tshogs las kyis skyed pa'o //
NG0504:1121: nyon mongs rags shing bsod nams phra //
NG0504:1122: mi dge rtag tu sdug bsngal ba'i //
NG0504:1123: rtsod ldan dus kyi snyigs ma lnga //
NG0504:1124: nyon mongs che la gnyen po chung *//
NG0504:1125: rmongs pa phyin ci log la gsal //
NG0504:1126: dus kyi snyigs ma 'gyur ldog che //
NG0504:1127: tshe thung nad mang blo bur 'chi //
NG0504:1129: nyon mongs dug lnga rang khar spyod //
NG0504:1130: dbang phyug sgyur smra'i chad lta 'dzin //
NG0504:1131: dge dman sdig pa dga' che bas //
NG0504:1132: mi lus thob kyang mi khom gnas //
NG0504:1133: skye rgas na 'chi'i rba la g.yeng *//
NG0504:1134: ma rig las kyi rnam shes de //
NG0504:1135: mi gtsang khrag gi mngal nas su //
NG0504:1136: tsha grang 'khyams rtags ris non pa'i //
NG0504:1137: sdug bsngal myong zhing 'jur mig la //
NG0504:1138: drangs pa'i tshul gyis skyes tsam na //
NG0504:1139: gsar gyur pags bshus gshed mas khyer //
NG0504:1140: sngangs skrag skye ba'i sdug bsngal myong *//
NG0504:1141: las kyi rnam smin lus po la //
NG0504:1142: phyi rol ltogs 'khyams ngal dub dang *//
NG0504:1143: mtshon dang 'byung ba dug gi nad //
NG0504:1144: rlung mkhris bad kan gdon 'dus kyi //
NG0504:1145: rtag tu lus la 'tshe nad mang *//
NG0504:1146: bu dang chung ma gnyen bshes tshogs //
NG0504:1147: 'brel pa dgra dang mnyam du gnod //
NG0504:1148: byams gnyen phan btags bral dogs brtser //
NG0504:1149: sdang dgra gnod skyal byas dogs dang *//
NG0504:1150: ma ldang ma phyid dogs pa yis //
NG0504:1151: med pa 'tshol ba'i sdug bsngal spyod //
NG0504:1152: yod pa 'tsho skyong zhen chags che //
NG0504:1153: mnga' rigs che chung gang yod @#//
NG0504:1155: sred pas dud 'gro bas kyang gdug / mi tshe ltogs dogs yid gdungs shing *//
NG0504:1156: yi dwags bzhin du bkres shing 'phongs //
NG0504:1157: chog shes med pa'i sdug bsngal la //
NG0504:1158: bde bar lta zhing sdug bsngal spyod //
NG0504:1159: grogs bshes gshin yul rnams dang bral //
NG0504:1160: dgra yi tshogs kyis bcom gyur te //
NG0504:1162: dus rnams kun tu bde ba med //
NG0504:1163: bzang po khengs shing grags pas myos //
NG0504:1165: phrag dog sma la mnyam pa yi //
NG0504:1167: ngan pa kun nas 'phongs pas nyen //
NG0504:1168: bde ba'i go skabs med pa la //
NG0504:1169: thar pa bsgrub 'dod gser bas dkon //
NG0504:1170: mi dge phra rags rdul bas mang *//
NG0504:1171: rnam rtog 'byung ba'i lus stobs bri //
NG0504:1172: phyi nang bde skyid dman par gyur //
NG0504:1173: lus nyams sems rmongs nad khams mang *//
NG0504:1174: mdangs shor tshe thung rgas pa'i dus //
NG0504:1175: snum zad me bzhin pha rol tu //
NG0504:1176: 'gro la khad de sdong rul bzhin //
NG0504:1177: gso thabs med pas kun gyis mnyam //
NG0504:1178: rgas pa'i sdug bsngal bsam mi khyab //
NG0504:1179: rgas pa zhum zhing stobs zad nas //
NG0504:1180: tshe dang srog dang drod 'gags pa //
NG0504:1181: nad gcod sdug bsngal zug rngu ni //
NG0504:1182: sha rus pags bral rtsa rgyus 'chang *//
NG0504:1183: srog snying rnam shes rten bur bral //
NG0504:1184: 'jig rten zhig pa'i dngangs skrag gis //
NG0504:1185: snying khrag po ste 'chi ba yi //
NG0504:1186: sdug bsngal bshad na glo snying 'brum //
NG0504:1187: rang snang rang rig ma shes pas //
NG0504:1188: snang med mun pa'i bar dor 'khyams //
NG0504:1189: dbang po kun tshang thogs med kyis //
NG0504:1190: snga phyi'i rigs mthun kun mthong ngo *//
NG0504:1191: ngo mi shes pas mun par 'thums //
NG0504:1192: khams gsum 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal spyod //
NG0504:1193: 'chi ba las zad tshe ma zad //
NG0504:1194: sdug bsngal blo bur rkyen gyis 'chi //
NG0504:1195: las zad tshe zad mnar nas 'chi //
NG0504:1196: de la bzlog thabs ma mchis pas //
NG0504:1197: bsod nams ma zad tshe zad 'chi //
NG0504:1198: nad med bde bar blo bur 'chi //
NG0504:1199: las ngan zad nas tshe zad 'chi //
NG0504:1200: tshe ring nad med bde bar 'chi //
NG0504:1201: blo bur tshe zad dge bas bzlog / lus sems rang bcud zad pa yi //
NG0504:1202: dus kyi tshe zad 'chi ba la //
NG0504:1203: sangs rgyas stong gi mthus kyang rdugs //
NG0504:1204: mdor na 'tsho rkyen yod pa na //
NG0504:1205: rgas kyang 'chi ba bsring du yod //
NG0504:1207: tsho la nges med sprin dang 'dra //
NG0504:1208: tshe 'di'i snang ba nub pa la //
NG0504:1209: 'chi ba zhes ni tha dad rtags //
NG0504:1211: mi lus don med glang gi snying *//
NG0504:1212: g.yeng bas mnar ba'i spre'u ste //
NG0504:1213: yun rings nad par gcong can 'dra //
NG0504:1215: khom ldan mi lus nyin mo'i dus //
NG0504:1216: skar ma bas kyang shin tu nyung *//
NG0504:1217: dge ba brtson pa'i 'du shes kyis //
NG0504:1218: tshul khrims sna re bsrungs pa yis //
NG0504:1219: ri rab gser nas 'phang du med //
NG0504:1222: phyid ni lha min gnas su bstan //
NG0504:1223: steng du bang rim bzhi po ni //
NG0504:1224: rin chen bzhi las grub pa yi //
NG0504:1225: khri phrag drug cu'i ri bo mdzes //
NG0504:1226: phyi rim ri bdun rol mtsho bdun //
NG0504:1228: phyogs kyi gtso bo rgyal chen bzhi'i //
NG0504:1229: gnas bzhi gnas 'khor bcu bcu steng *//
NG0504:1230: bzhi bcu gnas kyi 'og ma ni //
NG0504:1231: bang rim dang po'i 'phreng thogs nas //
NG0504:1232: skyabs song mchod sbyin dang byas rgyus //
NG0504:1233: phyogs dang zur dang mtha' gnas pa'i //
NG0504:1234: nyer mtsho dkar po thams cad dga' //
NG0504:1235: nags tshal yid 'ong nye ba'i tshal //
NG0504:1236: gnas bcu skor ba'i yul de la //
NG0504:1237: rin chen sna tshogs mdzes pa'i tshal //
NG0504:1238: me tog ljon shing du mas brgyan //
NG0504:1239: chu gtsang sbrang chang rgun 'brum chang *//
NG0504:1241: sgra snyan bya dang bung bas khengs //
NG0504:1242: rgyan gos longs spyod bza' btung rnams //
NG0504:1243: bsams pa tsam gyis 'byung ba dang *//
NG0504:1244: mdzes pa'i lha mo brgya phrag gis //
NG0504:1245: sna tshogs mchod pas mgu bar byed //
NG0504:1246: me long tshal du sngon gyi las //
NG0504:1247: snang 'gyur dran pas dga' bde skye //
NG0504:1248: rlung bzhin skad cig 'dod kun rgyug / 'dod pa'i
NG0504:1249: zhen pas dngos su 'khrig / bu tsha pha ma'i
NG0504:1250: mngal du ni // pha ma'i rtsib logs g.yas pa nas //
NG0504:1251: zhag bdun gnas te lo lnga'i tshul //
NG0504:1252: gos dang khang par bcas pa ru //
NG0504:1253: skyes nas zhag bdun nang du rdzogs //
NG0504:1254: 'phreng thogs la sogs lus kyi tshad //
NG0504:1255: rgyang grags bzhi cha gcig yin la //
NG0504:1256: rgyal chen bzhi ni rgyang grags phyed //
NG0504:1257: skyes te bde bar ldan par 'gyur //
NG0504:1258: gnyis pa lag na yol thogs ni //
NG0504:1259: tshul khrims dkon mchog mchod pa dang *//
NG0504:1260: dman pa'i 'gro la sbyin byas rgyus //
NG0504:1261: gzhan rnams sngon nas pad+ma'i nang *//
NG0504:1262: mdzes pa'i gzugs dang bung sgra snyan //
NG0504:1263: rlung gis dri zhim ro reg dga' //
NG0504:1264: yul lnga'i bde ba sbyor ba ni //
NG0504:1265: sngon las lhag ste rdzus skyes ldan //
NG0504:1266: 'khor lo sgyur ba dper bya min //
NG0504:1267: lha mo rnams dang lhan cig rtse //
NG0504:1269: de nas gsum pa rtag myos kyi //
NG0504:1270: gnas bcu gzhan la snod yangs shing *//
NG0504:1271: sdom ldan sbyin gnas skyob pa'i rgyus //
NG0504:1273: 'dod pa lnga yi longs spyod la //
NG0504:1274: snga ma gnyis pas bcu 'gyur lhag / yid kyi bde ba longs spyod ldan //
NG0504:1275: mdzes pa'i lha mo myos ma dang *//
NG0504:1276: bya dang bung ba bde bas myos //
NG0504:1277: me tog char 'bebs glu gar gyi //
NG0504:1278: sil snyan mchod pa bsam mi khyab //
NG0504:1279: khyad par dga' ba rtag tu 'phel //
NG0504:1280: de nas bzhi pa pi wang gnas //
NG0504:1281: rgyal chen bzhi ru skye ba'i rgyu //
NG0504:1282: kun dga' gnas dang mchod sbyin sogs //
NG0504:1283: dge 'dun zhabs thog brtson pa yis //
NG0504:1284: tshul ldan chos bkod pa las //
NG0504:1285: dri dga' shar nas yul 'khor skyong *//
NG0504:1286: dga' ldan 'phags skyes lho yi phyogs //
NG0504:1287: gzugs myos nub na mig mi @#//
NG0504:1289: lus ngan byang phyogs lcang lo can //
NG0504:1291: yid 'ong mdzes pa'i lha mo yis //
NG0504:1292: rtse zhing sgra snyan sgrogs par byed //
NG0504:1293: mdzes pa'i ri bo sna tshogs la //
NG0504:1294: mtshungs med me tog ljon pas brgyan //
NG0504:1295: bya dang bung ba gsung snyan sgrog / chu bsil 'bab chus ro bcur ldan //
NG0504:1296: sna tshogs 'dres pa'i dge ba yis //
NG0504:1297: sna tshogs mdangs ldan tshul du 'ong *//
NG0504:1298: tshal rnams kha dog spos so ste //
NG0504:1299: rang lus de yi kha dog 'gyur //
NG0504:1300: dper bya shel dang mtshungs pa yin //
NG0504:1301: rnam pa du ma'i bde ba yis //
NG0504:1302: yul drug myos par phyed pa yin //
NG0504:1303: phyir zhing srid pa cher 'ong bas //
NG0504:1304: srid pas ma tshim tshe zad nas //
NG0504:1305: gzhan du 'phos te las kyis ltung *//
NG0504:1306: de 'khor kun tu rgya ba'i lha //
NG0504:1307: bye ba gnas pa'i gzhal yas khang *//
NG0504:1308: sgron me phul ba'i sbyin stobs kyis //
NG0504:1309: mkha' la nyi zla gza' skar grags //
NG0504:1310: gling bzhi mun sel legs nyes ston //
NG0504:1311: nyi ma me shel drod kyi 'od //
NG0504:1312: dpag tshad lnga bcu rtsa gcig 'og / zla ba chu shel bsil gyi 'od //
NG0504:1313: dpag tshad lnga bcu gyen 'phang ste //
NG0504:1315: nang na skyed tshal grong khyer dang *//
NG0504:1316: dga' bas brgyan pa'i longs spyod ldan //
NG0504:1317: rang rtsal rlung gi shugs kyis 'khor //
NG0504:1318: rgya mtshor gnas pa'i rdzings bzhin du //
NG0504:1319: gzhal yas mi g.yo rlung nyid g.yo //
NG0504:1320: nam phyed nyi ma nub pa dang *//
NG0504:1321: nyi ma phyed dang 'char dus gcig / skar ma dpag tshad re re ste //
NG0504:1322: thams cad gzhal yas khang yin yang *//
NG0504:1323: de'i lha tshe zad 'chi ba'i dus //
NG0504:1324: gzhal yas khang zhig rgya mtsho'i nang *//
NG0504:1325: skar mda' ltung zhing klu rnams bkrag / 'di rnams
NG0504:1326: mi lo lnga bcu zhag / gcig tu rtsis pa'i
NG0504:1327: zla zhig ni // rang lo lnga brgya tshe yi tshad //
NG0504:1328: de nas mi dang lha yi tshad //
NG0504:1330: sum cu rtsa gsum skye ba'i rgyu //
NG0504:1331: dgra bcom pha ma mchod byed cing *//
NG0504:1332: tshul khrims skyon med sbyin pas 'grub //
NG0504:1333: brgya byin lha yi dbang po la //
NG0504:1334: bye ba stong gi lha mos mchod //
NG0504:1335: lhun po'i rtse mo brgyad khri'i steng *//
NG0504:1336: grong khyer chen po blta na sdug / bye ba'i dbus na chos bzangs gnas //
NG0504:1337: rnam par rgyal ba'i khang bzangs ni //
NG0504:1338: dpag tshad lnga brgya rin chen gyi //
NG0504:1339: gzhal yas nyi zla'i 'od bas gsal //
NG0504:1340: dpag med dga' ba'i tshal rnams dang *//
NG0504:1341: rin chen rdzing bu du ma rnams //
NG0504:1342: me tog tshogs kyi ra bas brgyan //
NG0504:1343: bung ba bya rnams mang pos gang *//
NG0504:1344: dri zhim ngad ldan mtshungs pa med //
NG0504:1345: rin chen bye ma brdal ba'i steng *//
NG0504:1346: khang bzangs brtsegs pa dpag tu med //
NG0504:1347: tshal dang nye ba'i tshal rnams dang *//
NG0504:1348: dus dang dus min zas dang gos //
NG0504:1349: lha yi rgyan rnams yid bzhin 'byung *//
NG0504:1350: rma bya ngang pa rta dang glang *//
NG0504:1351: lha yi byol song dga' bas rtse //
NG0504:1352: lha yi bu mos dga' bas mchod //
NG0504:1353: de sras lha kun bde bas khyab //
NG0504:1356: lha gnas grong khyer nyams dga' bar //
NG0504:1357: kha dog gzugs mdzes phun sum tshogs //
NG0504:1358: thams cad rin chen sa gzhi la //
NG0504:1359: gzhal yas khang mdzes skyed tshal dang *//
NG0504:1360: rin chen rdzing bu spos dang ldan //
NG0504:1361: me tog sna tshogs rab bkra zhing *//
NG0504:1362: ljon pa 'bab chu mdzes ldan dang *//
NG0504:1363: bza' btung rin chen snod rnams dang *//
NG0504:1364: rin chen khri gdan bkra ba'i gos //
NG0504:1366: bu mo mdzes ma du mas mchod //
NG0504:1367: dus 'da' yul lnga'i dga' bde spyod //
NG0504:1369: nyin mtshan cha ni gnyid mi gnyid //
NG0504:1371: bya skad sgrog mi sgrog gis 'byed //
NG0504:1372: lha dag gnas ni de rnams kyi //
NG0504:1373: shar phyogs shing rta sna tshogs tshal //
NG0504:1375: dga' bas brgyan pa byang na yod //
NG0504:1376: byang shar yongs su sa brtol shing *//
NG0504:1377: lho nub khrus kyis rdzing bu dang *//
NG0504:1378: nub byang a mo la ki rdo //
NG0504:1379: shar na chos bzangs mdun sa yod //
NG0504:1380: mtha' la lag na rdo rje'i gnas //
NG0504:1381: thugs rje las byung rnga bo che //
NG0504:1382: lha min gdug rtsub bzlog pa yis //
NG0504:1383: gzugs med chos kyi sgra sgrogs yod //
NG0504:1384: gnyis gnyis 'khyud nas dbang po sprad //
NG0504:1385: ma yi mngal du zhag bdun gnas //
NG0504:1386: byis pa lo drug lta bu skye //
NG0504:1387: de tshe ma mthong yul mthong bas //
NG0504:1388: ngo mtshar yid g.yo brtags dpyad byed //
NG0504:1389: rgyu de sngon gyi dge bar shes //
NG0504:1390: dga' zhing yi rang bag dang ldan //
NG0504:1391: lus kyi tshad ni rgyang grangs gcig / skyes nas zhag drug bar du rdzogs //
NG0504:1392: lha mo mdzes ma mang du 'byung *//
NG0504:1393: bde ba'i longs spyod tshogs kyis mchod //
NG0504:1394: bag med sred pas skye gnas brjed //
NG0504:1395: bslar zhing sred pas dus 'da' med //
NG0504:1396: dge ba'i las zad tshul min gyis //
NG0504:1397: lha yang sdug bsngal shin tu che //
NG0504:1398: 'jig rten gnas kyi mchog yin yang *//
NG0504:1399: 'phags pa ma gtogs sdug bsngal bas //
NG0504:1400: longs spyod sred pa'i le lo yis //
NG0504:1401: thar lam bral te tshe zad dus //
NG0504:1402: rang lo stong phrag gcig thub nas //
NG0504:1403: lha yi nye ba'i 'chi ltas lnga //
NG0504:1404: 'dod log skyes pas lha mo rnams //
NG0504:1405: gzhan gyis khyer zhing 'bros par byed //
NG0504:1406: khang bzangs rnams kyang 'jig la khad //
NG0504:1407: mdzes pa'i me tog 'phreng ba brnyings //
NG0504:1409: gos dang rgyan gyi kha dog nyams //
NG0504:1410: nges par 'chi ba'i rtags lnga las //
NG0504:1411: bza' btung thams cad rul ba dang *//
NG0504:1413: mi snyan sgra thos grogs kyis 'bor //
NG0504:1416: sngon chad med pa'i sdug bsngal 'byung *//
NG0504:1417: a tsa ma yi smre sngags 'don //
NG0504:1418: kye ma kyi hud 'dre log byed //
NG0504:1419: zhag bdun bar du sdug bsngal myong *//
NG0504:1420: dmyal ba bas kyang sdug bsngal che //
NG0504:1424: de mthong sdug bsngal bsran mi bzod //
NG0504:1425: de phyir thar pa ma thob na //
NG0504:1426: lha yi bde ba sdug bsngal dngos //
NG0504:1427: 'di la su zhig smon par byed //
NG0504:1428: lhag pa'i tshul khrims rnam pa bdun //
NG0504:1429: khyad par 'dod log spangs nas su //
NG0504:1430: pha ma nad pa chos smra la //
NG0504:1431: longs spyod byin zhing chos 'tshol ba //
NG0504:1432: ri rab nas ni drug 'bum khri //
NG0504:1433: brgya stong steng gi nam mkha' la //
NG0504:1434: rlung gis rin chen sprin phung bteg / de stengs mtshe ma'i grong khyer ni //
NG0504:1435: rab mdzes nyi shu rtsa bdun ni //
NG0504:1436: thams cad rin chen ri mchog steng *//
NG0504:1437: sum cu rtsa gsum gnas gzhi la //
NG0504:1439: dge ba'i las kyi mthu yin te //
NG0504:1440: de bzhin gnas rim de dag kyang *//
NG0504:1441: rin chen lnga las grub pa ste //
NG0504:1442: mtho ba dpag tshad stong phrag la //
NG0504:1443: dri med shel ltar 'od gsal zhing *//
NG0504:1444: rin chen ljon pa bkra ba la //
NG0504:1445: bza' btung gos dang rgyan rnams ni //
NG0504:1447: rin chen me tog du ma dang *//
NG0504:1448: bya dang bung ba sgra snyan 'byin //
NG0504:1449: bsam gyis mi khyab tshal bcas dang *//
NG0504:1450: rin chen khang pa brtsegs pa'i nang *//
NG0504:1451: lha bu re la lha mo stong *//
NG0504:1452: mdzes pa'i rnam 'gyur sil snyan sgra //
NG0504:1453: dri zhim ngad ldan bde ba myong *//
NG0504:1454: rma bya ngang pa shing rta zhon //
NG0504:1455: ri bo'i ngos dang mkha' la 'gro //
NG0504:1456: 'phags pa'i bya rnams chos sgra sgrogs //
NG0504:1457: bskul yang sred pa'i dbang du 'gro //
NG0504:1458: mi rtag de yi don mi rtogs //
NG0504:1459: bag med 'dod pa lnga la zhen //
NG0504:1460: de na rgyal ba'i thugs rje las //
NG0504:1461: rabs bdun rgyal ba'i mchod ten yod //
NG0504:1462: rin chen bdun las byas pa yi //
NG0504:1463: mdo rnams lha dbang ston par byed //
NG0504:1464: de yis bsod nams ldan pa'i lha //
NG0504:1465: bag yod chos spyod gong du 'phags //
NG0504:1466: lus sems can na myob pa las //
NG0504:1468: byis pa lo bdun lon 'dra skye //
NG0504:1469: sngon gyi skye gnas rjes su dran //
NG0504:1470: rgyang grags gcig dang bzhi cha gcig / zhag lngas tshad lus rdzogs pa yin //
NG0504:1471: bag med spyod pas skye gnas 'grib //
NG0504:1472: bag med lha rnams longs spyod bslus //
NG0504:1473: sngon gyi dge zad bde skyid nyams //
NG0504:1476: 'og tu ltung ste dmyal bas gtug / lha la smon pa'i bsam gtan 'khrul //
NG0504:1477: rang lo nyis stong tshe tshad rdzogs //
NG0504:1478: de las khyad 'phags dga' ldan ni //
NG0504:1479: sbyin sogs tshul khrims dag par bsrungs //
NG0504:1480: chos la sems pa'i byams pa yis //
NG0504:1481: lta bas yid smon byas pa yis //
NG0504:1482: dga' ldan gnas nyid nyams dga' ba //
NG0504:1483: dri med 'od kyi gzhal yas khang *//
NG0504:1484: sna tshogs mdzes pa reg na bde //
NG0504:1485: lha'i bu dri med zla mdzes la //
NG0504:1486: re re lha mo 'bum phrag bskor //
NG0504:1487: yid 'ong mdzes pa'i sgra dbyangs kyis //
NG0504:1488: mchod byas bde ba dpag tu med //
NG0504:1491: bdud rtsi chu bsil rdzing bu mdzes //
NG0504:1492: me tog kha dog dpe legs brgyan //
NG0504:1494: rin chen lhun po sna tshogs la //
NG0504:1495: ljon shing bya tshogs du mas gang *//
NG0504:1496: snyan pa'i sgra 'byin bar snang las //
NG0504:1497: sil snyan chos kyi rnga sgra sgrogs /
NG0504:1498: khang bzangs rin chen them skas can //
NG0504:1499: dril bu g.yer kha'i dra bas mdzes //
NG0504:1500: dri zhim spos kyi ngad ldan zhing *//
NG0504:1501: rin chen shing rta zhon nas su //
NG0504:1503: tshe rabs snga ma dran pa yod //
NG0504:1504: de na sngon gyi smon lam mthus //
NG0504:1505: 'phags pas sprul pa'i lha rnams yod //
NG0504:1506: rgyal sras mi 'pham mgon po bzhugs //
NG0504:1507: byang chub lam la 'god par mdzad //
NG0504:1508: phyogs bcur sprul pa bsam mi khyab //
NG0504:1509: bde ba che la lha rnams bskul //
NG0504:1510: 'khor lo bskor ba bla na med //
NG0504:1511: 'dod pas myos pas lha rnams ni //
NG0504:1512: lag bcangs reg pa tsam gyis tshim //
NG0504:1513: zhag bzhi lo brgyad tshul gyis skyes //
NG0504:1514: lus tshad rgyang grags phyed dang gnyis //
NG0504:1515: mngal nas dus bzhin tshad lus rdzogs //
NG0504:1516: de tshe sngon gyi dge dran spyod //
NG0504:1517: bsod nams ldan rnams pad+ma la //
NG0504:1518: rdzus skyes ting nge 'dzin la gnas //
NG0504:1519: tshe lo stong phrag bzhi thub bo //
NG0504:1520: rang gi rtsol ba'i nga rgyal gyis //
NG0504:1521: rkyen las ma ltos rang 'khrul ba'i //
NG0504:1522: sbyin sogs tshul khrims dge ba rnams //
NG0504:1523: sngon las lhag pa'i 'bras bu yi //
NG0504:1525: brgya byin 'bum pas bde stobs lhag / rin chen sna tshogs sa gzhi la //
NG0504:1526: ri bo ljon shing me tog dang *//
NG0504:1527: skyed tshal sna tshogs mdzes par bskor //
NG0504:1528: gzhal med khang chen khri stan dang *//
NG0504:1529: dri mchog gdugs dang ba dan dang *//
NG0504:1530: gos dang 'phreng ba rgyan rnam pa //
NG0504:1531: rol mo sil snyan du ma dang *//
NG0504:1532: zhal zas ro brgya ldan pa'i bcud //
NG0504:1533: rang gis bsams pa tsam las su //
NG0504:1534: 'dod pa rang gi sprul pa ste //
NG0504:1535: lha mo 'bum phrag mang po dang *//
NG0504:1536: rgod cing reg pas yid tshim byed //
NG0504:1537: lag tu me tog gtad pa tsam //
NG0504:1538: zhag gsum pad+ma'i nang nas su //
NG0504:1539: lo dgu lon pa lta bu skye //
NG0504:1540: lus tshad rgyang grags phyed dang gnyis //
NG0504:1541: zhag gsum rdzogs te sngon la dran //
NG0504:1542: dpag med 'dod yon lnga spyod cing *//
NG0504:1543: dregs pa'i nga rgyal zhen pa rnams //
NG0504:1544: stobs ldan bdud dbang rigs su 'gyur //
NG0504:1545: de rnams lha dbang zlog par byed //
NG0504:1546: dga' ldan gnas las khyad 'phags kyang *//
NG0504:1547: 'phags pa ma yin lha rnams tshal //
NG0504:1548: 'dod yon bde la sred pa yis //
NG0504:1549: sngon gyi dge zad dus 'das te //
NG0504:1550: nye dang ring ba'i 'chi ltas bcu //
NG0504:1551: byung ste nyams nas ngan song lhung *//
NG0504:1552: tshe ni rang lo stong phrag brgyad //
NG0504:1553: 'dod pa gzhan gyi ster ba yi //
NG0504:1554: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed skye ba'i rgyu //
NG0504:1555: sbyin dang tshul khrims bzod la sogs //
NG0504:1556: ma nyams skyon med bsrungs ba'i mthus //
NG0504:1559: khyad 'phags lha yi rigs su skye //
NG0504:1560: 'chi khar log ltas mtshams sbyor ba //
NG0504:1561: bdud rigs rnams su skyes pa yis //
NG0504:1563: log lta spangs pa'i dge ldan pa //
NG0504:1564: gzhan la dbang byed stobs dang ldan //
NG0504:1565: dbang sgyur lha yi gzhal yas khang *//
NG0504:1566: rin chen bye ma brdal ba'i ljongs //
NG0504:1567: ri bo brtsegs pa'i steng na //
NG0504:1568: kun gsal 'od kyi khang pa ni //
NG0504:1569: gru bzhi gru mang them skas dang *//
NG0504:1570: skar khung ba gam du mas mdzes //
NG0504:1571: lha yi rol mo du mas spras //
NG0504:1573: mar gad ra ga sbug la sogs //
NG0504:1575: skyed tshal rdzing bu me tog bcas //
NG0504:1577: bza' btung gos dang rgyan mchog dang *//
NG0504:1578: dri mchog phye ma 'phreng ba dang *//
NG0504:1579: sil snyan snyan pa'i sgra dbyangs kun //
NG0504:1580: 'dod khams kun las 'di nyid lhag / khang bzangs la sogs lha mo rnams //
NG0504:1581: re re 'od dang kha dog gzugs //
NG0504:1582: mdzes pa'i glu gar rtsed mo rnams //
NG0504:1583: 'jig rten gsum na ma mchis pas //
NG0504:1584: chags phral mgon po ma gtogs pa //
NG0504:1586: ltas pa tsam gyis 'khrig pas tshim //
NG0504:1587: lag mthil me tog pad+ma'i nang *//
NG0504:1588: bu tsha lo bcu'i rnam pa skye //
NG0504:1589: lus kyi tshad ni rgyang grags gnyis //
NG0504:1590: zhag gnyis nang du tshad lus rdzogs //
NG0504:1591: sngon shes sngon gyi dge ba dran //
NG0504:1592: de nas gzhan dag lha mo yis //
NG0504:1593: 'dod yon lnga gter bag med kyi //
NG0504:1595: nam zhig sred pas chags sdang skye //
NG0504:1596: mi dge bdud kyi bsam pa 'char //
NG0504:1597: 'chi ltas lnga tshang bdud kyis dbang *//
NG0504:1598: las kyis mnar bas na rag spyod //
NG0504:1599: de las ldog pa'i lha rnams ni //
NG0504:1600: 'phags pa'i blo ldan bsam gtan gnas //
NG0504:1601: zhen pa med pa'i bde la spyod //
NG0504:1602: rang lo khri dang drug stong thub //
NG0504:1603: pho mo'i gzugs can 'dod pas 'khrig / 'dod chags bzhi yi srid pa la //
NG0504:1605: bde ba rags pas 'dod khams pa //
NG0504:1606: de ru skye ba'i gzugs can rnams //
NG0504:1607: kun rdzob gos dang khang par bcas //
NG0504:1608: 'dod pas skye ba gsum yin no //
NG0504:1609: 'chi ba ma gtogs lha rnams la //
NG0504:1610: skye rgas na ba'i sdug bsngal med //
NG0504:1611: sngon gyi dge ba'i 'bras bu yin //
NG0504:1612: bsod nams zad pa'i rnam smin gyis //
NG0504:1613: 'chi khar mnar med pas kyang sdug / lhun po'i steng na gnas pa yi //
NG0504:1614: 'dod lha'i bde ba sdug bsngal te //
NG0504:1615: las kyi yid byed 'khrul pa yin //
NG0504:1616: 'khor ba dag na bde ba med //
NG0504:1618: gzugs kyi khams gnas bcu bdun la //
NG0504:1619: gzugs la gzung bas gzugs khams pa //
NG0504:1620: dug gsum 'dod zhen bral ba yi //
NG0504:1621: sbyin dang tshul khrims gtsang ma'i gnas //
NG0504:1622: bzod pa bsam gtan cher gnas pas //
NG0504:1625: dge ba sngon pas dag par spyod //
NG0504:1627: chags zhen sred pa'i rgyur mthong nas //
NG0504:1628: de nyid spong 'dod bsam gtan la //
NG0504:1629: zhen pas mtshams sbyar tshangs rigs skyes //
NG0504:1630: spro bas tshangs pa'i mdun na 'don //
NG0504:1631: gzhan phan yod pas tshangs chen du //
NG0504:1632: chung 'bring chen po'i bsam gtan de //
NG0504:1633: gti mug dang ldan 'khor ba ste //
NG0504:1635: de rnams rdzus skyes gos dang bcas //
NG0504:1636: bzod pas gzugs bzangs phun sum tshogs //
NG0504:1637: tshangs rigs lus tshad dpag tshad phyed //
NG0504:1638: dpag tshad gcig gnyis rim pas rdzogs //
NG0504:1639: rin chen sna tshogs 'od kyi zhing *//
NG0504:1640: mtho dman med pa'i mnyam pa nyid //
NG0504:1641: tshangs pa'i gzhal med khang chen ni //
NG0504:1642: 'dod khams rin chen kun las lhag / de 'od sus kyang sgrib mi nus //
NG0504:1643: chos kyi sil snyan sgra mi 'chad //
NG0504:1644: pho dang mo yi ming yang med //
NG0504:1645: dpag med longs spyod ldan gyur yang *//
NG0504:1646: 'dod pa med de bde ba'i ngang *//
NG0504:1647: gnyid dang nyin mtshan rtog pa bral //
NG0504:1648: bsam gtan zas kyi dga' ba spyod //
NG0504:1650: 'dod khams sdug bsngal gnas su mthong *//
NG0504:1651: nyi ma srin bu me khyer mtshungs //
NG0504:1652: tshangs pa'i rgyal po 'di yis ni //
NG0504:1653: rgyal ba rnams la chos gsung bskul //
NG0504:1654: de phyir mi mjed bdag po zhes //
NG0504:1655: khyad par 'phags pa'i lha yin no //
NG0504:1656: phyin ci log rnams log par lta //
NG0504:1657: gzugs khams lha rnams thun mong du //
NG0504:1658: lus rdzogs gos dang gzhal yas khang *//
NG0504:1659: bcas pa 'og min bar du yin //
NG0504:1660: thun mong ma yin bsam gtan khyad //
NG0504:1661: gong mas gong ma khyad du 'phags //
NG0504:1662: bsam gtan gnyis pa rtog med bsgom //
NG0504:1663: 'od chung du skyes sngon pas lhag / lus kyi tshad ni dpag tshad bzhi //
NG0504:1664: spro dga' dang bcas bsgom pa las //
NG0504:1665: dpag tshad brgyad gzugs tshad med 'od //
NG0504:1667: lus la dpag tshad bcu drug go / 'di rnams gnas ni dngos 'dzin med //
NG0504:1668: 'od snang las grub gzhal yas yin //
NG0504:1669: shin tu dga' bde bsam gtan spyod //
NG0504:1670: tshim par gyur pa'i zag bcas yod //
NG0504:1671: de nas dga' bde zhen pa bral //
NG0504:1672: shes bzhin rtse gcig rig pa las //
NG0504:1673: bsgom pa bsam gtan gsum pa'i don //
NG0504:1674: dge chung bstan byas tshad med dge //
NG0504:1675: bstan pa thob pas dge rgyas skyes //
NG0504:1676: lus tshad rim bzhin so gnyis dang *//
NG0504:1677: ro zhing brgya dang nyi shu brgyad //
NG0504:1678: bsam gtan dben pas gang bsams 'grub //
NG0504:1679: mtshungs med 'od kyi gzhal yas na //
NG0504:1681: rang bzhin rtogs pa ma bral bas //
NG0504:1682: gzung 'dzin nyon mongs gting na zhen //
NG0504:1683: zag pa zad na 'phags lam ste //
NG0504:1684: bsam gtan bzhi par skye ba'i rgyu //
NG0504:1685: rnam rtog tshogs la mi g.yo bsgom //
NG0504:1688: dpag tshad nyis brgya lnga bcu'o //
NG0504:1689: de nyid goms stobs bsod nams skyes //
NG0504:1690: lus la dpag tshad lnga brgya yod //
NG0504:1692: lus la dpag tshad lnga brgya yod //
NG0504:1693: lus la dpag tshad stong gnas te //
NG0504:1694: nyon mongs bag la nyal ba yod //
NG0504:1695: 'jig rten kun rtog ma bral bas //
NG0504:1696: nam zhig bsod nams las zad mthus //
NG0504:1697: nyon mongs skyes nas dus 'da' byed //
NG0504:1698: don shes bsam gtan 'phags lam bgrod //
NG0504:1699: shes rab mi ldan bsam gtan ni //
NG0504:1700: g.yang sar gnas pa'i dmus long de //
NG0504:1701: gnas chos 'thur ma ltung ba bzhin //
NG0504:1702: srid pa'i ngan song g.yang la ltung *//
NG0504:1703: bsam gtan gnas pa'i lha kun ni //
NG0504:1704: gnas skabs tsam gyi bde ba ste //
NG0504:1705: 'khor bar ldog pa'i bsam gtan yin //
NG0504:1706: bsam gtan bzhi pa'i lha rigs cig / 'du shes bkag nas dben pa byed //
NG0504:1708: nam zhig 'du shes sad pa dang *//
NG0504:1709: phyir zhing log ltas mtshams sbyar nas //
NG0504:1710: mkha' la rgyu ba'i yi dwags te //
NG0504:1711: tshe ring lha rnams mnar med skye //
NG0504:1712: mi khom brgyad gnas 'gro ba yin //
NG0504:1713: bsam gtan rdzun pas thar mi thob //
NG0504:1714: gtsang ma rigs kyi lha lnga po //
NG0504:1715: nyon mongs zag bcas bral ba yis //
NG0504:1716: sbyin sogs dge bas skyed pa las //
NG0504:1717: bsam gtan shes rab cha dang 'brel //
NG0504:1718: nyon mongs cha che mi che ba //
NG0504:1719: nyon mongs cha chung mi gdung ba //
NG0504:1720: bral bas gya nom snang ba dang *//
NG0504:1721: bsam gtan gnas pas shin tu mthong *//
NG0504:1722: dbang thob 'og min lus kyi bar //
NG0504:1723: nyis stong bzhi stong brgyad stong dang *//
NG0504:1724: khri dang drug stong sum khri dang *//
NG0504:1725: nyis stong lus kyi tshad yin no //
NG0504:1726: tshe tshad tshangs rigs bskal chung ni //
NG0504:1727: nyi shu de bzhin bzhi bcu dang *//
NG0504:1728: tshangs chen lnga bcu rtsa brgyad dang *//
NG0504:1729: 'od chung bskal chen gcig yin no //
NG0504:1730: de nas yar la bcu bcur 'phel //
NG0504:1731: sngon dge tshe tshad ring ba yin //
NG0504:1732: de rnams rang snang gzhan snang gi //
NG0504:1733: gzugs dang gzhal yas khang dang bcas //
NG0504:1734: ri rab la brten lha gnas yin //
NG0504:1735: gzugs med rten la ma chags par //
NG0504:1736: bdag tu 'dzin la chags pa yi //
NG0504:1737: bar snang sprin bzhin gnas pa ste //
NG0504:1738: rgyu ni bsam gtan bzhi la brten //
NG0504:1739: gzugs kyang nyon mongs rtog par mthong *//
NG0504:1740: gzugs kyi 'du shes bkag nas su //
NG0504:1741: nam mkha' lta bur dmigs bcas pas //
NG0504:1742: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched de //
NG0504:1743: rang gzugs mi snang mkha' lta bu //
NG0504:1744: rnam shes sna tshogs skye mched la //
NG0504:1745: rtog tshogs 'du shes bshig pa yin //
NG0504:1746: rnam shes mtha' yas skye mched de //
NG0504:1747: rtog pa med pa'i 'du shes la //
NG0504:1748: ci yang ma yin skye mched de //
NG0504:1749: yod pa nyid la med dmigs nas //
NG0504:1750: ci yang med rtog de bshig pas //
NG0504:1751: yod min med min skye mched do //
NG0504:1752: sems nyid mtha' bral lhun grub las //
NG0504:1755: nyon mongs can yid gang dang gang *//
NG0504:1756: goms pa'i snang ba de nyid la //
NG0504:1757: gnas skabs de dang der snang ba //
NG0504:1758: nyer dmigs zhi ba'i nga rgyal tsam //
NG0504:1759: ji ltar lha yi bde ba yang *//
NG0504:1760: chab rom steng gi bzhin du //
NG0504:1761: dus tshod gcig la ma tshor 'jig / shes rab zin na 'phags pa'i lam //
NG0504:1762: 'dod gzugs bral bas zhi yin yang *//
NG0504:1763: bag chags ma dag 'khor ba ste //
NG0504:1764: shes rab med kun 'og tu ltung *//
NG0504:1765: tshe ni bskal pa nyi khri dang *//
NG0504:1766: bzhi khri drug khri brgyad khri thub //
NG0504:1767: skyes pa de yi snang ba shar //
NG0504:1769: de ltar gang du skyes nas yang *//
NG0504:1770: skye shi'i las dang nyon mongs kyi //
NG0504:1771: sdug bsngal rba la 'dzad pa med //
NG0504:1772: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bstan pa gzhi'i rgyud mchog rin po che sbungs pa las //
NG0504:1773: 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o ///
NG0504:1774: / ma rig 'du byed skyen pa yi //
NG0504:1775: sdug bsngal srid pa'i rgya mtsho na //
NG0504:1776: ma srid pa ni gang yang med //
NG0504:1777: ma la bu skye kun gyi chos //
NG0504:1778: bu la ma skye ka rta ste //
NG0504:1779: chu las skyes nas zhag bdun ni //
NG0504:1780: ma med tshe yi dus byed la //
NG0504:1781: rang gi kha nas ma skyes te //
NG0504:1782: ma yis khar mid khong du song *//
NG0504:1783: zhag bdun ma yi mngal du sdod //
NG0504:1784: lus rdzogs spyir thon ma yis g.yos //
NG0504:1785: ma dang mnyam du chu la 'phong *//
NG0504:1787: kye ma 'dus byas rnam smin dag / skye shi 'jig pa'i chos can te //
NG0504:1788: snod bcud mi rtag chags 'jig stong *//
NG0504:1789: phyi yul mi rtag dus gzhi 'gyur //
NG0504:1790: nang lus mi rtag skye rgas 'chi //
NG0504:1791: snang ba mi rtag rmi lam 'dra //
NG0504:1792: byas chos mi rtag sgyu ma bzhin //
NG0504:1793: yul mkhar mi rtag dri za'i grong *//
NG0504:1794: dgra gnyen mi rtag tshong dus 'gron //
NG0504:1795: zas nor mi rtag sbrang bu'i rtsi //
NG0504:1796: sgyu lus mi rtag chu bur 'dra //
NG0504:1797: bzhin mdog mi rtag bar snang 'ja' //
NG0504:1798: tshe 'di mi rtag nam mkha'i glog / btsan po mi rtag ri gzar dbab //
NG0504:1799: dngos po mi rtag nam mkha'i sprin //
NG0504:1800: 'dod yon mi rtag smi sgyu chu //
NG0504:1801: gtan po mi rtag 'khyag thog mkhar //
NG0504:1802: snga phyi mi rtag ston ka'i rab //
NG0504:1803: skye shi mi rtag chu yi rba //
NG0504:1804: rang gzhan mi rtag rtswa kha'i zil //
NG0504:1805: bzang po mi rtag shi ba'i ro //
NG0504:1806: mtho dman mi rtag chu khyer shing *//
NG0504:1807: 'du byed mi rtag gar mkhan bzhin //
NG0504:1808: gcig tu mi rtag sna tshogs 'gyur //
NG0504:1810: 'jig rten mi rtag zog dang gsob //
NG0504:1811: 'dus byas rkyen gyis sna tshogs bsgyur //
NG0504:1812: sdug bsngal min pa gcig kyang med //
NG0504:1814: thog med dus nas da lta'i bar //
NG0504:1815: nyon mongs dbang gis skye shi ni //
NG0504:1816: yang nas yang du lus blangs pa //
NG0504:1817: dpag med rdul gyi grangs pas mang *//
NG0504:1818: sems can gcig gi lus la yang *//
NG0504:1819: yang yang blangs pas bsgrang mi lang *//
NG0504:1820: sha rus bsags na sa rdo tsam //
NG0504:1821: rnag khrag bsags na rgya mtsho bas //
NG0504:1823: bar song yang don med yod //
NG0504:1824: gzhan gyi lus blangs lta ci smos //
NG0504:1825: snga ma shi ba'i ro mthong na //
NG0504:1826: phyi ma skye ba glo snying 'dar //
NG0504:1827: 'khrul pa'i rtsa ba ma chod na //
NG0504:1828: las kyi skye ba chu rdol bzhin //
NG0504:1829: srid pa'i skye sgo mi khegs pas //
NG0504:1831: ma rig chu bos shugs kyis 'khyer //
NG0504:1832: sdug bsngal skye shi'i rba la g.yeng *//
NG0504:1833: zad cing stongs pa'i dus mtha' med //
NG0504:1834: sems can nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NG0504:1835: 'khrul pa'i glong na tshad gzung dka' //
NG0504:1837: rang gis rang 'khrul smyon pa bzhin //
NG0504:1838: gcig tu mi gnas 'khrul pa'i blo //
NG0504:1839: ma rig zhing gi sa bon la //
NG0504:1841: dge sdig las kyi so nam gyis //
NG0504:1842: 'bras bu bde sdug mtho dman ni //
NG0504:1843: nges med rnam pa sna tshogs pa //
NG0504:1844: las kyi 'khrul 'khor rlung gis bteg / rigs drug 'khor ba'i grong khyer du //
NG0504:1845: mi dge las dang nyon mongs kyi //
NG0504:1846: rgyu gnyis rkyen gsum mtshams sbyar nas //
NG0504:1847: gnag pa'i rnam smin rgyu rkyen gyis //
NG0504:1848: ngan song gsum du sdug bsngal spyod //
NG0504:1849: mnar med gnas su yun rings 'khyams //
NG0504:1850: dkar ba'i rgyu rkyen 'bras bu yi //
NG0504:1851: lha mi'i gnas rnams ma lus skyes //
NG0504:1852: lung ma bstan pa'i btang snyoms kyis //
NG0504:1853: byol song mun pa'i gnas su 'khyams //
NG0504:1854: rnam pa sna tshogs gzugs mang la //
NG0504:1855: sdug bsngal mi 'dra dpag med myong *//
NG0504:1856: lhar skyes gson por ngan song ltung *//
NG0504:1857: lha min grong khyer rang gis bsreg / mi yi rgyal po grong sprang byed //
NG0504:1858: seng ger skyes nas gzhan gyis zos //
NG0504:1859: yi dwags zas kyis brnangs nas shi //
NG0504:1860: dmyal ba rang gi srog gcod byed //
NG0504:1861: ma ni chu ru 'gyur ba yi //
NG0504:1862: mi rtag 'gyur ba'i chos can la //
NG0504:1863: nges med log pa'i sdug bsngal 'byung *//
NG0504:1866: mnar med gnas na zhen yun ring *//
NG0504:1867: las zad tshe na 'dam nas thon //
NG0504:1868: skam sar snyogs pa srid pa tsam //
NG0504:1869: 'khor ba'i chu bo gting zhen che //
NG0504:1870: sdug bsngal rba glong sna tshogs 'khrul //
NG0504:1872: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bstan pa gzhi'i rgyud mchog rin chen spungs pa las //
NG0504:1873: 'dus byas mi rtag par bstan pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o ///
NG0504:1874: / skye med gzhi rtsa ma chod pas //
NG0504:1876: gcig nas gcig rgyud lu gu rgyud //
NG0504:1877: rgyun chad med pa chu bo'i rgyun //
NG0504:1878: sdug bsngal chu bo'i gnyer ma 'dra //
NG0504:1879: phyi ma skyes pas snga ma 'gag / skye shi gnyis la zad pa med //
NG0504:1880: gcig nas 'pho zhing gcig tu skye //
NG0504:1881: 'chi kha'i shes pas mtshams sbyar nas //
NG0504:1882: phyi ma de yi snang bar skye //
NG0504:1883: dge sdig gnyis kyi bzang ngan la //
NG0504:1884: sngar gyi bag chags sbyangs stobs kyis //
NG0504:1885: goms pa 'chi khar des mtshams sbyar //
NG0504:1886: blo bur rkyen gyis gzhan 'gyur na //
NG0504:1889: bzang po'i las ni bzang po 'thud //
NG0504:1890: ngan pa las ni ngan pa 'thud //
NG0504:1891: gnas skabs rkyen gyi 'khrul pa byung *//
NG0504:1894: gzhi ma dkar po gcig nyid la //
NG0504:1895: tshon rtsis kha dog bsgyur ba bzhin //
NG0504:1896: kun gzhi rnam shes snam bu la //
NG0504:1897: rgyu rkyen gnyis kyis snang ba bsgyur //
NG0504:1898: chu bo chu bran lu ma rnams //
NG0504:1900: gang byas chu gzhun gcig pa bzhin //
NG0504:1901: bde sdug btang snyoms gang snang yang *//
NG0504:1902: ma rig 'khrul pa'i rgyun du gcig / bde chen ye shes ma rtogs na //
NG0504:1903: sdug bsngal chu bo rgyun mi 'chad //
NG0504:1904: 'di phyi bar dos mtshams sbyar nas //
NG0504:1905: 'khor ba zo chu'i khyud mo bzhin //
NG0504:1906: rgyun chad med par khor yug byed //
NG0504:1907: nam zla dros pa'i dus kyi tshe //
NG0504:1908: drod gsher gnyis kyi rkyen las su //
NG0504:1909: sa bon byed mkhan med par skye //
NG0504:1910: myu gu 'bras bu skye ba bzhin //
NG0504:1911: sems can rigs mthun 'dzom pa'i tshe //
NG0504:1912: las dang nyon mongs rgyu rkyen gyis //

NG0504:2047: dud 'gro la sogs chung bo yin //

NG0504:2056: bsam pa med par mtshon shor ba //
NG0504:2057: dbang med shugs kyis shi ba rnams //
NG0504:2058: sdig tu mi 'gyur srog gcod yin //
NG0504:2059: gzhan rnams rang gi srog dang mtshungs //

NG0504:2061: pha rol bdag tu gzung ba'i rdzas //
NG0504:2062: mi dga' bzhin du blangs pa'o //
NG0504:2063: dbye ba stobs kyis phrogs pa dang *//
NG0504:2064: rgyu yis dkris par spyad pa dang *//

NG0504:2069: gzhan dag tshul ni gong ltar ro //

NG0504:2071: sdig tu mi 'gyur ma byin len //
NG0504:2072: gzhan dag rang gi rdzas dang 'dra //

NG0504:2076: yi dwags bkres skom gnas su skye //

NG0504:2078: rang ngam gzhan gyi chung ma la //
NG0504:2079: gnas ma yin par spyod pa'o //
NG0504:2080: dbye ba rigs dang chos dang khrims //
NG0504:2081: bsrung ba rim pa gsum yin no //

NG0504:2083: bdag pos bzung ba 'bring pos te //
NG0504:2084: phal pa rnams ni chung ngu'o //
NG0504:2086: gzhan rnams rang gi lus dang mtshungs //

NG0504:2097: mi chos bla ma mgo bskor rdzun //
NG0504:2098: mchod 'os bslus pa rdzun chen la //

NG0504:2105: dge 'dun dbyen byas chen po ste //
NG0504:2106: gang zag dkrugs pa 'bring yin la //

NG0504:2168: dbang gis gang la yid ches mos //
NG0504:2169: rnam smin chos med mun par skye //
NG0504:2170: yang na skad cig mnar med ltung *//

NG0504:2255: bsod nams ye shes bsngos pa na //

NG0504:2266: mnar med dmyal ba su yis byas //

NG0504:2291: so nam sgyu ma'i ston thog mtshungs //
